            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "NumPy uses the IEEE Standard for Binary Floating-Point for Arithmetic\n(IEEE 754). This means that Not a Number is not equivalent to infinity."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
